{"tid":2370870,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不知為何被捕 - 高慧然","createTime":"2021-01-18T10:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T11:50:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58279f75f466b8cd99d69b8d7f614b79dd083191","tid":2370870,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210118/NKJBHXWX4NGKHKIT76OK4DELGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210118%2FNKJBHXWX4NGKHKIT76OK4DELGA%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=3cd7d400\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210118%2FNKJBHXWX4NGKHKIT76OK4DELGA%2F&h=aff9aa09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210118/NKJBHXWX4NGKHKIT76OK4DELGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不知為何被捕 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gwshBBIX-zI18ppzaQpcf0DCODE=/1161x715/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SK3QSLIDSVAYNNP7GKKA4U76NQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgwshBBIX-zI18ppzaQpcf0DCODE%3D%2F1161x715%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSK3QSLIDSVAYNNP7GKKA4U76NQ.png&h=53fa2a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桐叔黃國桐律師無端被捕，扣押超過40小時之後，終獲保釋。身為律師的黃國桐，對自己被捕一事感到莫名其妙，用「百思不得其解」形容發生在他自己身上的事。但強調會繼續在自己的崗位做自己深信及認為自己該做的事。<br />\n<br />\n一個熟知法律的律師，尚且不知自己觸犯了哪條法律，因何被捕，其他從未讀過法律，缺乏法律專業知識的尋常香港人，又可以如何避免突然被捕的命運呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果肥佬黎不被噤聲，讓他面對公眾說幾句，他可能也會撓撓頭說「百思不得其解」。以租務糾紛為名，把他送入囚牢，未審先判。明明涉嫌民事案件，卻鐵鏈纏身，視他為江洋大盜。他犯了甚麼法？他不知道，其他香港人不知道，他的律師可能也不知道。<br />\n<br />\n《國安法》籠罩之下的香港，每。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港人為甚麼要逃離香港？就是為了要逃離這種「不知為何被捕」的命運。BNO逃離潮已成定局，正如WhatsApp無法阻止使用者轉投Signal的懷抱。不要問人心為何背離，先問自己為何令人死心、絕望。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：kowaiyin.yoyoko"},{"pid":"c944d8486ad466e684eeb5f4e1b4265d35945d13","tid":2370870,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"人人都唔知 但其實人人都知"},{"pid":"d455c30a2370cda40de00122264028236eeff8a6","tid":2370870,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">各大愛蚑尤其肥佬黎，做得&quot;中國人&quot;居然唔尊重芝麻第一非物質文明&quot;莫須有<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;？？？</span></span></span></strong>"}]}